<h1>About Us?</h1>

<h3>Welcome to By the Campfire</h3>

<p>

    <p>This is a multi-authored collection of random literature, stories, and musings by a close-knit group of friends, namely: Ned, Miguel, and Dwight. Ned decided to build this site since he knows the specific kind of "literature" required to put a web page together (coding).</p>
    
    <p>Here, you will read posts from the three of us (or more, if anyone wants to join!). We have all agreed to use our pen names rather than our real identities.</p>
    
    <p>If you'd like to join us around the bonfire, kindly disturb @ned and send him a message.</p></p>